    <div class="info">
      <p> The Beagle is a small dog that weighs roughly 20-30 pounds and lives for an average of 10-15 years. They have a short coat length and are described as curious, friendly and merry. </p>

      <p> <a href="https://www.akc.org/dog-breeds/beagle/"> See more information about the Beagle from the American Kennel Club. </a> </p>

